            <thetext>Currently, SQLAnalyzer only provides syntax highlighting for SQL files. PlainAnalyzer is used to make the symbols searchable. Instead, we should create a custom symbol tokenizer like the other analyzers do. Definitions (reported by ctags) are ignored, both in the index and in the xref. We should add the definitions to the index and also handle them in the xref.</thetext>
